About this item

  • Efficient fan: powerful blower with a fan speed of 2400 RPM for an air flow of 395 CFM. Moves air through your target location efficiently for optimal ventilation, effectively circulates air for room ventilation and odor purification
  • Low noise and speed control: durable plastic fan housing and blades for extremely low noise(<35 dB). Have a variable speed controller, you can adjust it to desired airflow level according to your requirement
  • Easy installation: removable duct ends with locking tabs for quick removal and easy maintenance. Universal mounting bracket for direction of airflow indicating
  • Multifunctional: suitable for industrial, household and horticulture ventilation applications, help you maintain a healthy grow room. Ideal solution for multi-purpose use in residential and commercial ventilation
  • Note: max ambient temp is 104/40. Package included: 1 pack 6 inch inline duct fan with speed controller

From the manufacturer

iPower Ventilation Combo

Low Noise

  • Durable plastic fan housing and blades for extremely low noise.
  • Motor features a permanently lubricated bearing that operates quietly and requires no maintenance.

Efficient Fan

  • Move air through your target location efficiently for optimal ventilation, effectively circulates air for room ventilation and odor purification.
  • Reduce humidity, clear the air and lower temperatures in grow rooms.

Speed Control

  • Have a variable speed controller, you can adjust it to desired airflow level according to your requirement.
  • Perfect for grow tents, greenhouses, hydroponics, kitchens, bathrooms, basements, locker rooms, garage.

Versatile Applications

Product Description

Widely used: suitable for industrial, household and horticulture ventilation applications, help you maintain a healthy grow room. Ideal solution for multi-purpose use in residential and commercial ventilation.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Garret
3.0 out of 5 stars 6" Fan With Controller
Reviewed in the United States on April 21, 2023
Size: 6'' Fan with Speed ControllerVerified Purchase
I've been using this fan with a 6ft long 6in duct to pull cold air into an office full of heat producing computers. For my use case, it has worked pretty well. I was hoping that it would be a bit quieter, and while it's really hard to move a lot of air quietly, the 35dB claimed on the page is way off. At best (when set to it's lowest speed), I'm able to measure 60dB from 3ft away using a calibrated sound level meter. At the highest speed, I measure 65dB at the same distance. I knew that 35dB couldn't be right for a fan this size, but I was really hoping for something in the low 50's that could be blocked easily with headphones. I'm also skeptical of the 395CFM airflow spec, but I don't have the equipment to measure that accurately.
